in the far south.
   Last Aug. 24, the navy delivered to local newspapers a series of
pictures that it said showed four Soviet trawlers making illegal
catches in southern Chilean waters.
   The navy said in the future that it will take ``drastic
measures'' against those trawlers, including seizing the vessels.
